# E-Voting System (C++)

A console-based Electronic Voting System built in C++ using file handling for persistent storage of candidates, voters, and votes.

## Features
- Voter registration and secure login
- Candidate management (add/remove/view)
- Encrypted vote casting
- Admin panel for results and vote management
- Colorful console UI with loading animations

## Tech Stack
- Language: C++
- Storage: File handling (no external database)

## Project Structure

evoting-system-cpp/
├── main.cpp
├── candidate.h / candidate.cpp
├── voter.h / voter.cpp
├── vote.h / vote.cpp
├── utils.h / utils.cpp

## How to Build & Run
```bash
g++ main.cpp candidate.cpp voter.cpp vote.cpp utils.cpp -o evoting
./evoting
```

## How to Use
1. Register as a voter
2. Login with your Voter ID and password
3. Cast your vote for a candidate
4. Admin can view results via the Admin Panel

